title: $5,500, First time on Market!  Beautiful 2 bd/2ba ensuite Nob Hill
map_address: 1439 Leavenworth Street near Jackson and Washington
posting_body: ['GORGEOUS sun-drenched 2-bedroom, 2 bath ensuite apartment located near the top of Nob Hill one street from the famous Cable Car route and within a block of Hyde Street and all the many restaurants and bars of Russian Hill.', ' Turn the opposite direction and you are at the top of Nob Hill, more restaurants and bars within easy walking distance to the Financial District, lively North Beach, and Chinatown.', ' Trader Joe’s is a couple of blocks away.', 'Fully restored  7-unit building built to the highest standards providing each resident with private and sophisticated living.', ' Never before occupied.', 'Walk Score for this address:', '• Walk Score: 99', '• Transit Score: 83', '• Bike Score: 61', 'Amenities:', '•\tKitchen:  Chef’s kitchen with stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinets, Carrera Marble countertops with bar seating.', '•\tLiving Room:  Very spacious, open-concept living room with lots of windows, awash in light, French Oak wide plank hardwood floors throughout.', '•\tBedrooms:', '•\tMaster bedroom with  ensuite bathroom clad in  Carrera marble and subway tiles.', '•\tSecond bedroom with double pocket doors, ensuite bathroom in Carrera marble and subway tiles.', '•\tLaundry:  In unit washer AND dryer', '•\tFlooring:  Wide-plank French Oak', 'Additional Features:', '•\tUtilities:  Water and Garbage covered', '•\tLaundry:  In unit', '**Covid and Shelter-In-Place compliant in person apartment showings allowed.', 'Set up an appointment today.', '**', 'Contact Information:', '•\tApplication Fee:  $45 (18+)', '•\tContact:  Patty Szeto via email or text', 'Please reference LEA03CL when inquiring, and provide your contact information', '•\tManager:  Renee Engelen DRE Broker #010879547', '•\tEqual Housing Opportunity', "•\tRenter's Insurance required", '•\tNo Pets', '•\tNo smoking building', '*** Pictures are representative of floorplans and units within the building.', 'Some photos may be from other units.', '***']
